This '''temple''' was the headquarters of the [[Imperial Mission]] based on [[Socorro/Legends|Socorro]] as of [[137 ABY]].

The temple was razed by [[Darth Talon]] when she was sent by [[Darth Krayt]] to capture [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Marasiah Fel]]. [[Elke Vetter]] perished within the temple, having [[Duel on Socorro|fought]] and been defeated by Talon, giving the Princess time to flee the planet.

